content:
Strength:
Power Clean 3-3-3-3-3
Push Press 5-5-5

Metcon:
"Death by Burpee-Box-Jumps"
Minute 1 - 1 Burpee-box-jumps
Minute 2 - 2 Burpee-box-jumps
Minute 3 - 3 Burpee-box-jumps
...... and so on until you run out of time,  tap out or make it twenty rounds.
If you fail to get required number of Burpee-box-jumps in a minute – start over at 1 and go up the ladder again. Continue for 20 minutes.
